The Debian Package rsnapshot-scripts
----------------------------

* rsnapshot-backup-mysql:
	- Create a backup user with a strong password and give them
	the following global priviledges SELECT, SUPER, SHOW DATABASES,
	LOCK TABLES. This will allow them to backup your data without
	modifying it if the account is breached.

